// Configuration settings file for Time of Life — Release / production.
// API base URL is injected via Info.plist so runtime code can read it.

// xcconfig treats `//` as a comment, so we break it with an empty variable.
// The $(EMPTY) reference expands to nothing, resulting in
// https://timeoflife-api.antonkosenko.pro (the Cloudflare-fronted origin).
EMPTY =
API_BASE_URL = https:/$(EMPTY)/timeoflife-api.antonkosenko.pro